edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamond.Exception
This package encapsulates all the exception classes we create in the game.

This package encloses all the unit test classes.
edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamondConnectionManager
This package implements messengers classes to send message and manage messages on both server side and client side.
edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamondConnectionManager.Command
This package encapsulates all the command classes that send between server and clients.

This is the package for all the basic cards in the game.

This package contains the details of different types of cards.
edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamondModel.Card.CharacterCards

This is the package for all the resource cards in the game.
